Raw material: single crystal of Ba(Fe 0.935 Co 0.065 ) 2 As 2 pnictide
Sentence: Isothermal magnetic field dependence of magnetization and the magnetic relaxation measurements were performed for H c axis on single crystal of Ba(Fe 0.935 Co 0.065 ) 2 As 2 pnictide superconductor having T c = 21.7 K.
A detailed study of isothermal magnetic field dependence of the magnetization, M (H), and the magnetic relaxation, M (t), on a Ba(Fe 0.935 Co 0.065 ) 2 As 2 single crystal is presented.
